---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Yukun — Micro Motion Solutions | Yukun" description="Yukun (Shenzhen) Supply Chain Technology — your partner for precision micro drive solutions. 20+ years manufacturing, ISO 9001, 1-week samples.">
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Yukun</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-12">
        Your global partner for precision micro drive solutions — from concept to production.
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none
        [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:mb-4
        [&_h3]:text-xl [&_h3]:font-semibold [&_h3]:mt-8 [&_h3]:mb-3
        [&_p]:text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] [&_p]:leading-relaxed
      ">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Yukun (Shenzhen) Supply Chain Technology Co., Ltd. is a specialized provider of micro drive
          solutions — DC gear motors, brushless DC motors, micro pumps, and micro switches. We partner
          with world-class manufacturing facilities in China's Pearl River Delta to deliver engineered
          solutions for product developers worldwide.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are not a catalog seller. We organize our products by <strong>your application</strong> —
          medical devices, smart locks, EV charging, robotics, and more — and provide engineer-level
          selection support to match the right drive to your specific requirements.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border-default)] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🎯</div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Solution-First</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">We start with your application, not a parts list. The right motor for a smart lock is different from the right motor for a surgical robot — even if they share the same diameter.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border-default)] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⚡</div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Speed</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Engineering recommendations in 24 hours. Evaluation samples in 1 week. Production in 2-4 weeks. We respect your development timeline.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border-default)] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔧</div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Custom Without the Premium</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Custom shaft, encoder, connector, mounting — standard on every order. No "minimum customization fee." No "special project pricing."</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Quality & Manufacturing</h2>
        <p>Our manufacturing partners operate:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>20+ years of micro motor manufacturing experience</li>
          <li>30,000 m² ISO 9001:2015 certified facility</li>
          <li>IATF 16949 certification for automotive-grade production</li>
          <li>150,000-200,000 units daily capacity</li>
          <li>100% outgoing load testing per unit</li>
          <li>Full material traceability and batch performance recording</li>
          <li>RoHS & REACH compliant materials</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Global Reach</h2>
        <p>
          We ship worldwide from Shenzhen, China — FOB, CIF, or DDP as you prefer. Our team handles
          export documentation, customs clearance, and logistics coordination so you can focus on
          your product development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
